After completing it,
she moved into

39:34.570 --> 39:37.994
a brand-new and fully-paid-for
apartment in Georgetown,

39:38.040 --> 39:40.736
and took a plum appointment
at the Department of Labor.

39:40.770 --> 39:42.829
It was rather a rapid ascent,
wouldn't you say?

39:42.880 --> 39:44.006
You found her price.

39:44.040 --> 39:45.007
Didn't you?

39:45.050 --> 39:46.142
She'd've had to find

39:46.180 --> 39:47.875
some of your recent conquests

39:47.910 --> 39:49.741
and pay them off to come
forward, of course, but...

39:49.780 --> 39:51.077
I assume she offered
a generous package.

39:53.090 --> 39:54.751
So, why are you here?

39:54.790 --> 39:56.018
You want me to tell the cops

39:56.060 --> 39:57.755
that I paid her
to go to bed with me?

39:57.790 --> 39:59.428
HOLMES: It would help
us prove our case.

