identify the people

40:05.700 --> 40:06.997
that Michelle is paying
to come forward.

40:07.030 --> 40:08.759
But when the arrest is made,

40:08.800 --> 40:11.530
then everything I did
goes public.

40:11.570 --> 40:13.902
Mm.

40:16.910 --> 40:18.878
Let me ask you something:

40:18.910 --> 40:21.208
Suppose there is no arrest.

