or...

40:40.270 --> 40:43.034
I'll go to press.

40:43.070 --> 40:45.630
What about your job, Gareth?

40:45.670 --> 40:47.535
You'll be ruined, too.

40:47.570 --> 40:49.231
I don't let murderers
go free, you see?

40:49.280 --> 40:53.068
It's probably the only
non-negotiable thing about me.

40:55.150 --> 40:56.640
Besides, you know,
I've been

40:56.680 --> 40:59.114
ruined before.

41:01.020 --> 41:04.558
Not so bad
the second time around.

41:04.590 --> 41:07.058
Sorry about the chair.

41:07.090 --> 41:09.194
Regulations for a discharge.

41:09.230 --> 41:10.993
Your car's downstairs.

41:11.030 --> 41:12.622
We'll have you at the airport
in plenty of time.

41:12.670 --> 41:15.059
Thanks for everything,
Guillermo.

41:16.140 --> 41:18.529
