Michelle Forrester...

41:18.570 --> 41:20.538
you're not leaving New York.

41:20.570 --> 41:22.572
Just yet.

41:24.310 --> 41:27.643
WATSON: Are you sure
they're ready for this?

41:27.680 --> 41:29.739
It's not the sort of thing
